System Requirements for Project Sparrow

The Sparrow System is a drone flight system that will be able to take flight and navigation commands from a flight planner (not a radio controller or manual flight). It will be able to navigate via GPS positioning and complete a pre-defined flight plan
The Sparrow System shall support manual flight mode with FPV video feed
The Sparrow System shall have a minimum flight time of 20 minutes
The Sparrow System shall comply with FAA regulations on drone usage
